1
00:00:00,690 --> 00:00:05,330
The most powerful daily prayer for any time and before meditation,

2
00:00:05,330 --> 00:00:09,490
which is the order from God and Supreme Master Ching Hai,

3
00:00:09,950 --> 00:00:12,310
shares with us by his blessed grace.

4
00:00:12,830 --> 00:00:24,100
We humbly worship, praise, thank, obey and love God Almighty,

5
00:00:24,840 --> 00:00:33,390
the Most High, the Greatest, for world vegan, world peace and our soul liberation.

6
00:00:34,050 --> 00:00:40,940
We thank, love, praise the only Son of God,

7
00:00:40,940 --> 00:00:45,760
who is the ultimate Master for our salvation.

8
00:00:46,980 --> 00:00:51,200
We follow the teaching of all the saints and sages.

9
00:00:52,280 --> 00:00:55,340
We thank, love and praise them,

10
00:00:56,120 --> 00:01:02,480
who are the representatives of God for our spiritual elevation.
